						               													<description>Boba Boss is a fast-paced, brain-twisting, color and word association game. The game is crazy simple and easy to figure out. It takes less than a minute to learn and even less time than that to play it. A round can be over in mere seconds!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Boba Boss can be played with 2 to 6 people, but packing the table to the max is more fun. Everyone plays as an employee at a boba tea shop. Your goal is to win employee of the minute, by filling all of your your seven tea cups before anyone else finishes filling theirs. Complicating the situation a little is the fact that not only are players filling their own cups, they&amp;rsquo;re also spilling their opponents cups at the same time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game cleverly employs the stroop effect to test players' deciphering abilities and reaction times. Insani-tea is  inevitable and that's a big part of the fun. The cute boba ball theme and the delightfully simple game play make this game accessible to most anyone who isn't afraid to rub elbows at the table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do you have what it takes to become the Boba Boss?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
